# No AI attribution in git or copy

Never add git commit trailers or metadata that reference AI tools, including:

- `Co-authored-by: Cursor`
- `Co-authored-by: Claude`
- `cursoragent@cursor.com` or similar agent emails
- Any `Co-authored-by` line for an AI assistant

All commits must be attributed only to Rayann Sagnon.

Do not mention Cursor, Claude, or other AI assistants in user-facing copy, README credits, or contributor sections unless the user explicitly asks.
